rComments: One of the best TAs I have ever had. I had her for both PSYB07 and PSYC08. Gelareh is very nice and approachable and always takes the time to help the students. She is very good at explaining difficult stats concepts and I found her marking to be easy and very fair. I switched from another tutorial to be in her section.
Had Gelareh as a TA for PSYC08, she's easy on the eyes but a HARD MARKER!

This class unexpectedly turned out one of the best for me! I really like how she incorporated the lifespan approach to this course; this class was the first one that got me genuinly interested in journal articles and cognitive psychology; I really like her approach and her personality. Highly recommend!
